            <td><div class="price-labor">$175–$340</div><div class="price-parts-note">+ latch motor or thermal fuse</div></td>
            <td>Door latch motor, thermal fuse (blown by self-clean heat), control board.</td>
          </tr>
          <tr >
            <td><div class="repair-type">Control board / display failure </div><div class="repair-desc">Display dead, error codes, erratic behavior</div></td>
