            <td><div class="price-labor">$89</div><div class="price-parts-note">Applied to repair</div></td>
            <td>Applied to labor when you approve. Includes gas pressure check on gas wall ovens.</td>
          </tr>

        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
    <p class="table-note"><strong>All prices are labor only.</strong> Parts quoted separately. Quote before we start; invoice matches the quote. 90-day warranty on parts and labor.</p>
  </div>
</section>
